# News Sentiment Analysis API with FastAPI & Machine Learning

## Overview

Project ini adalah implementasi sederhana Machine Learning menggunakan:

* FastAPI
* Scikit-learn
* Docker
* NLP TF-IDF
* Logistic Regression

untuk melakukan sentiment analysis pada berita saham/news Indonesia.

Model dapat memprediksi sentiment:

* positive
* negative
* neutral

Dataset menggunakan:

[https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/triagungj/cnbc-indonesia-stock-news-sentiment-dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/triagungj/cnbc-indonesia-stock-news-sentiment-dataset)

---

# Features

* FastAPI REST API
* Machine Learning sentiment analysis
* TF-IDF text vectorization
* Logistic Regression classifier
* Dockerized application
* Automatic model training
* Evaluation result export
* Swagger API documentation
* Confidence score prediction
* Indonesian news sentiment dataset

---

# Tech Stack

* Python 3.12
* FastAPI
* Scikit-learn
* Pandas
* Docker
* Uvicorn

