# Installation

## 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone
cd project
```

---

# 2. Download Dataset

Download dataset dari Kaggle:

[https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/triagungj/cnbc-indonesia-stock-news-sentiment-dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/triagungj/cnbc-indonesia-stock-news-sentiment-dataset)

Rename file menjadi:

```text
